gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 116, Cavaliers 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Cavaliers 116-109. Moritz Wagner recorded 22 points (12 in the fourth quarter) along with seven rebounds for the Magic, with Franz Wagner adding 14 points, four rebounds, and four assists in the victory. Jarrett Allen tallied 18 points and 10 rebounds for the Cavaliers in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 31-25, while the Cavaliers fall to 36-18.
